You love this company more than I do.

89
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:49,560
I just hope the company won't collapse

90
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,159
and the families

91
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,400
of my several hundred employees

92
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,860
can still enjoy the happiness of festivals.

93
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,040
And don't become a pig.

94
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,900
Or the company will collapse.

95
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:04,360
The company might really collapse.

96
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:09,040
Mr. Zhu, forgive me for being nosy.

97
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:12,480
Is Ms. Hou the flawless girl your mom mentioned?

98
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,040
Yes.

99
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,360
