112
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,840
What are you doing?

113
00:06:10,470 --> 00:06:11,640
Trying my best.

114
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:14,140
If we don't solve the problem of you becoming a pig after sunset,

115
00:06:14,140 --> 00:06:15,390
the company will go bankrupt.

116
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,020
By then, I won't be able to

117
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:18,000
turn on colorful lights for all the kids in the world

118
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,400
or pay my rent next month.

119
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,850
