172
00:08:22,530 --> 00:08:24,640
Every day of our relationship is an anniversary.

173
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,220
There should be rituals in life.

174
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:27,280
Oh.

175
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:32,380
