244
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:51,830
First of all, you're handsome.

245
00:12:52,380 --> 00:12:54,180
Secondly, you are independent.

246
00:12:54,260 --> 00:12:56,770
You could've relied on your father, but you worked on your own.

247
00:12:56,770 --> 00:12:58,610
You started from scratch and endured all the hardships.

248
00:12:58,610 --> 00:13:00,230
