249
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:02,110
and didn't plagiarize it.

250
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,100
Your temper

251
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,120
is not very bad.

252
00:13:06,470 --> 00:13:08,190
