264
00:13:39,500 --> 00:13:40,380
Praise.

265
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,950
Your hairstyle today

266
00:13:44,620 --> 00:13:45,880
makes you look better.

267
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:47,810
It makes you look young.

268
00:13:48,700 --> 00:13:51,820
Do I usually look old?

269
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:55,350
And your outfit is good. It shows your good parts

270
00:13:55,350 --> 00:13:58,240
and covers the other parts, making you look well-proportioned.

271
00:13:58,240 --> 00:13:59,680
It makes you look slim.

272
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,480
I'm not fat.

273
00:14:02,860 --> 00:14:04,520
Your makeup is also very good.

274
00:14:05,830 --> 00:14:07,600
It makes you look less depressed

275
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,850
and more energetic.

276
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,990
Zhu Xiaoyang, you are a pig.

277
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,880
I am...
